msgstr ":guilabel:`Unikatowość na podstawie`: `E-mail (Lead/Szansa)`"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation/target_audience.rst:64
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Filter`: :guilabel:`Match` :guilabel:`all 🔽 (down "
